# APIPerfScanner - API Speed and Error Analyzer

APIPerfScanner is a developer-friendly CLI tool to detect slowdowns or response anomalies across multiple APIs.

## Features
- Parallel scan engine  
- Logs latency + error codes  
- Output to CSV / JSON  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_APIPerfScanner.git
cd 21_APIPerfScanner
python monitor.py
